    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0771b08"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000027091">襄州夾石山</placeName><persName key="A010439">思公</persName>傳（<persName key="A010441">曇真</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0771b09"/><persName key="A010439">釋思公</persName>，姓李氏，<placeName key="PL000000002384">恒陽</placeName>人也。早出家于本府<placeName key="PL000000002370">龍<lb
ed="T" n="0771b10"/>興寺</placeName>。得度後，遊<ref type="place" target="#PL000000023581">伊洛間</ref>，見<persName key="A009319">普寂禪師</persName>，開暢<lb
ed="T" n="0771b11"/>禪法。<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>始見提誘，尋徹鉤深。至<placeName key="PL000000027119">南雍</placeName>，隱<placeName key="PL000000027091">夾<lb
ed="T" n="0771b12"/>石山</placeName>，翛然自處。屬<persName key="A010440">牛公</persName>觀政<placeName key="PL000000027770">漢南</placeName>，聞其聲<lb
ed="T" n="0771b13"/>績，請入城，謝病不應其命。<persName key="A010440">牛帥</persName>亦不奪<lb
ed="T" n="0771b14"/>其志，檀施相望。學眾侁侁，若栴檀之圍遶<lb
ed="T" n="0771b15"/>焉。以<date from-iso="0784" key="j20074402007535" to-iso="0784">興元初年</date>示疾歸滅，春秋八十四焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0771b16"/><placeName key="PL000000016485">毫州安國院</placeName><persName key="A010441">釋曇真</persName>，姓陳，<placeName key="PL000000021111">維青</placeName><note resp="sgsz">案查無「維青」之地。《新脩科分六學僧傳．卷五》作「濰青」。疑為「<placeName key="PL000000021111">青州</placeName>」別稱。</note>人也。少小隨<lb
ed="T" n="0771b17"/>父往<placeName key="PL000000009523">彭<anchor xml:id="beg0771002"/>城<anchor xml:id="end0771002"/></placeName>，鬻棗於逆旅，而亡所怙。<persName key="A010441">真</persName>嘆<lb
ed="T" n="0771b18"/>恨無依，乃投<placeName key="PL000000009509">徐大雲寺</placeName>為僧。其土是<persName key="A005407">嵩法<lb
ed="T" n="0771b19"/>師</persName>之後，經論藪澤，真翫習該通。後遊勝境，<lb
ed="T" n="0771b20"/>入<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName>學禪觀。已至<placeName key="PL000000021318">任城</placeName>，邂逅<persName key="A010442">李中丞諷</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0771b21"/>赴職<placeName key="PL000000016494">譙郡</placeName>，接真談道，抵掌盱衡，如披雲霧。<lb
ed="T" n="0771b22"/><persName key="A010442">李</persName>恨相識之晚，請以同行。時聚風亭月觀，談<lb
ed="T" n="0771b23"/>道達旦。<persName key="A010442">李</persName>後入為<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189">京</ref>尹，因從容稱奏<persName key="A010441">真</persName>道<lb
ed="T" n="0771b24"/>成德至。<persName key="A004215">德皇</persName>下詔徵，而不奉詔。<date from-iso="0791-05-12" key="j20100982010126" to-iso="0791-06-09">貞元七年<lb
ed="T" n="0771b25"/>四月</date>示滅，門人建塔云。</p>
